</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Batman Beyond - The Eggbaby</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Terry McGinnis has to take care of a futuristic Eggbaby to avoid failing a Family Studies class. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EggSitting" class='trope-example-link'>Egg Sitting</a></p>
</div>
